HEADWORD: Intertex
<hw>In`ter*tex"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>intertexere</ets>; <ets>inter</ets> between + <ets>texere</ets> to
weave.]</ety> <def>To intertwine; to weave or bind together.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
